Place commercial Live2D model folders here.

Each model folder should contain:
- A .model3.json file with the same name as the folder
- .moc3, .physics3.json, and other required Live2D files
- Motion files (*.motion3.json) directly in the model folder or in a motions/ subfolder
- Expression files (*.exp3.json) directly in the model folder or in an expressions/ subfolder
- Sound files (*.wav, *.mp3, *.ogg) directly in the model folder or in a sounds/ subfolder

Example structure:
Commercial_models/
  YourModel/
    YourModel.model3.json
    YourModel.moc3
    YourModel.physics3.json
    idle.motion3.json
    happy.exp3.json
    sound.wav

